TriggerPortal-Unreal.h/cpp
--------------------------
Trigger Box actor that has the ability to "teleport" players
back some distance. This effect is covered using UE4's 
fog which increases when the trigger is entered.

Interactive Fog Blueprint - Unreal.PNG
--------------------------------------
Blueprint code that uses TriggerPortal's information to 
increase the density of in game fog only when the player
is in one of the TriggerPortals and vice versa.
